<font size="64">- What is it now? - What is this?</font>

4078
01:40:23,360 --> 01:40:25,360
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Mysterious items handed over to them)</font>

4079
01:40:25,160 --> 01:40:28,090
<font size="64">- We should predict the season. - Should I go all-in on one season?</font>

4080
01:40:25,490 --> 01:40:28,090
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Sell whatever is in season.)</font>

4081
01:40:28,090 --> 01:40:29,090
<font size="64">I'll invest in winter.</font>

4082
01:40:28,960 --> 01:40:31,730
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The signal flare launched by the tiger moths)</font>

4083
01:40:29,090 --> 01:40:30,660
<font size="64">I have to go all-in. I have no choice.</font>

4084
01:40:30,660 --> 01:40:31,860
<font size="64">I'll sell them all.</font>

4085
01:40:31,830 --> 01:40:34,600
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(A psychological war among traders with no trust)</font>

4086
01:40:31,860 --> 01:40:33,070
<font size="64">Did they do something? What are they doing?</font>

4087
01:40:33,070 --> 01:40:34,630
<font size="64">I didn't think of that. Hang on.</font>

4088
01:40:34,600 --> 01:40:35,600
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Big player)</font>

4089
01:40:34,630 --> 01:40:35,730
<font size="64">I bought 11.</font>

4090
01:40:35,600 --> 01:40:36,800
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ready to make dangerous deals...)</font>

4091
01:40:36,400 --> 01:40:37,440
<font size="64">I'll give you a fan.</font>

4092
01:40:36,800 --> 01:40:38,340
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(just to catch the perfect timing)</font>

4093
01:40:37,440 --> 01:40:38,470
<font size="64">- A fan? - Take it.</font>

4094
01:40:38,470 --> 01:40:40,010
<font size="64">- I'll lose on purpose for you. - Okay.</font>

4095
01:40:40,010 --> 01:40:42,110
<font size="64">- Write the season I want. - Okay.</font>

4096
01:40:42,010 --> 01:40:44,110
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The suffocating money war of the tiger moths)</font>

4097
01:40:42,110 --> 01:40:43,780
<font size="64">- I don't like you. - I'm upset.</font>

4098
01:40:43,780 --> 01:40:45,480
<font size="64">Just let me take a breath.</font>

4099
01:40:45,480 --> 01:40:46,710
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Either they make a fortune,)</font>

4100
01:40:45,480 --> 01:40:46,710
<font size="64">He went all-in on winter.</font>

4101
01:40:46,710 --> 01:40:49,010
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(or it all turns into worthless scraps.)</font>

4102
01:40:46,710 --> 01:40:48,510
<font size="64">Excuse me. I spent 70 dollars.</font>

4103
01:40:48,510 --> 01:40:50,380
<font size="64">He's just a thief!</font>

4104
01:40:50,280 --> 01:40:54,350
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Who will be the winner to flip their life around with one choice?)</font>

4105
01:40:50,380 --> 01:40:51,780
<font size="64">Don't be like this, sir.</font>

4106
01:40:52,580 --> 01:40:54,090
<font size="64">Hey! Seriously...</font>

4107
01:40:54,090 --> 01:40:55,720
<font size="64">Seriously, So Min.</font>

4108
01:40:54,650 --> 01:40:59,120
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Solo Money-up)</font>

4109
01:40:55,720 --> 01:40:58,720
<font size="64">- Well done! - This is so upsetting.</font>

4110
01:40:59,320 --> 01:41:05,060
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Running Man)</font>

